      "notes": "I entirely made up Dema Clearwater, but I saw the name in one of my research books and decided  it would be nice to have a common ancestress for the Clearwater family. No, she did not have a husband, and no one knows who fathered her kids (and there's a high chance her kids are actually half-siblings).\n\nI also invented a few more branches and siblings, which I find personally fun. And then I filled in some gaps as far as who Brady Fuller's parent is, and how Emily is related to Leah. Had to google what second cousins look like on a tree\n"
    },
