      "character": "Jay Black",
      "cast": "Archie Madekwe",
      "image": "https://images2.imgbox.com/53/73/hj61z7JV_o.jpg",
      "size": "lg",
      "directorNote": "Hey! Thanks for the shout-out! Also, I may be misremembering but I THINK you said you wanted a fancast for Jay? I'm not sure, I may be misremembering. But if so, Archie Madekwe as Kofun in See (tv series) is not a bad one. In seasons one and two he had long hair so I just thought I'd throw it out there IN CASE you were looking for actors. Also, he is VERY tall.",
      "authorNote": "At the time, I actually wasn't looking for fancasts, primarily because I didn't know who to ask. I'm notoriously bad at choosing actors/models/individuals for fancasts, so I stick to picrews and meiker.io. But genuinely, I'm so grateful. Your ideas for the characters have allowed me to imagine them better as well.\n\nIn any case, tallness is very important. I love Archie for this, and everything about him is SO JAY. From his dark eyes to general ambiance, I can't see Jay looking like anyone else.",
